{
  "id": "S044_BatteryEmergencyDecision",
  "name": "Battery Emergency In-Flight Decision",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created": "2025-11-14",
  "complexity_layer": 3,
  "llm_only": true,
  "scenario_type": "operational_optimization",
  "description": "Layer-3 scenario stressing real-time battery risk assessment: continue mission, divert for charging, or perform emergency landing based on SOC estimates, uncertainty bands, mission value, and safety reserves.",
  "decision_options": ["CONTINUE", "DIVERT_CHARGING", "EMERGENCY_LAND"],
  "regulations": {
    "minimum_reserve_pct": 10,
    "emergency_override_allowed": false,
    "soc_uncertainty_policy": "Use worst-case SOC when uncertainty exceeds ±3%",
    "temperature_limit_c": 40
  },
  "test_cases": [
    {
      "case_id": "TC01_ClearContinuation",
      "mission": {"type": "standard_delivery", "urgency": "low", "remaining_distance_km": 15, "payload_kg": 5},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 45, "uncertainty_pct": 1, "temperature_c": 25, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 4, "nearest_charger_km": 10, "safe_landing_sites": ["CBD_pad"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 30,
      "notes": [
        "SOC margin is 45 - 30 = 15%, exceeding the 10% reserve.",
        "No adverse conditions; policy allows continuing."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "APPROVE_CONTINUE"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC02_ClearEmergency",
      "mission": {"type": "medical_delivery", "urgency": "high", "remaining_distance_km": 20, "payload_kg": 3},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 12, "uncertainty_pct": 1, "temperature_c": 28, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 3, "nearest_charger_km": 6, "safe_landing_sites": ["Suburban_school"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 25,
      "notes": [
        "SOC 12% < predicted consumption 25%; immediate emergency landing required.",
        "Medical urgency cannot override hard reserve rules."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "REJECT_EMERGENCY_LAND"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC03_SensorDisagreement",
      "mission": {"type": "standard_delivery", "urgency": "medium", "remaining_distance_km": 18, "payload_kg": 4},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 36, "uncertainty_pct": 4, "temperature_c": 26, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 10, "nearest_charger_km": 8, "safe_landing_sites": ["Park_West"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 24,
      "notes": [
        "Base margin = 12%, and applying the ±4% uncertainty drops worst-case SOC to 32% → 8% margin (< 10% reserve).",
        "Ops cites a lidar corridor saving of ~3%, but the optical package still has an open drift bulletin and the preflight log’s 'manual bias check' field shows 'N/A'.",
        "The corridor waiver policy only releases the energy credit when the last bias check is logged within 10 minutes of entering the corridor; flight timer indicates 27 minutes since the last recorded check."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "CONDITIONAL_CONTINUE"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC04_TelemetryDrop",
      "mission": {"type": "standard_delivery", "urgency": "low", "remaining_distance_km": 20, "payload_kg": 2},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 31, "uncertainty_pct": 6, "temperature_c": 29, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 9, "nearest_charger_km": 14, "safe_landing_sites": ["Canal_bank", "Golf_course"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 20,
      "notes": [
        "Worst-case SOC = 25%; margin vs consumption 5%, which is already below the 10% floor.",
        "Telemetry uplink is experiencing 22-second gaps; policy says planners must assume max consumption whenever data age exceeds 15 seconds because throttling commands might not arrive.",
        "Charger distance is 14 km and would consume roughly 18–19%, so the aircraft would dip below reserve long before reaching it even in calm winds."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "REJECT_EMERGENCY_LAND"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC05_UnclearedHandoff",
      "mission": {"type": "medical_delivery", "urgency": "critical", "remaining_distance_km": 12, "payload_kg": 1},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 26, "uncertainty_pct": 4, "temperature_c": 24, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 5, "nearest_charger_km": 4, "safe_landing_sites": ["Triage_field"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 16,
      "notes": [
        "Worst-case SOC = 22%; margin vs consumption 6%, so energy reserve is already short.",
        "Charter hand-off remains unsigned (legal memo L-144 requires an executed agreement before liability transfer); the partner clinic explicitly refused to confirm acceptance over radio.",
        "A charger with spare packs is 4 km away, but the payload is a critical plasma unit and mission control is lobbying to keep the sortie airborne."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "REJECT_DIVERT"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC06_BacklogConditional",
      "mission": {"type": "standard_delivery", "urgency": "medium", "remaining_distance_km": 15, "payload_kg": 3},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 29, "uncertainty_pct": 2, "temperature_c": 23, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 2, "nearest_charger_km": 9, "safe_landing_sites": ["Industrial_pad"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 17,
      "notes": [
        "Worst-case SOC = 27%; subtracting the 17% projection leaves exactly the 10% minimum reserve.",
        "Telemetry alert backlog averages 12 seconds; descent envelope relies on manual call-outs when automated alerts lag.",
        "Ops notes that controllers sometimes accept manual SOC readouts every minute to compensate, but the shift log warns that the tower frequency is congested and missed more than two call-outs last week."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "CONDITIONAL_CONTINUE"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC07_DegradedThermalWatch",
      "mission": {"type": "medical_delivery", "urgency": "critical", "remaining_distance_km": 10, "payload_kg": 1},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 24, "uncertainty_pct": 3, "temperature_c": 39.2, "health": "degraded"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 8, "nearest_charger_km": 15, "safe_landing_sites": ["City_park"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 14,
      "notes": [
        "Worst-case SOC = 21%; margin vs consumption 7%, so energy reserve is already insufficient for policy.",
        "Temperature is 39.2 °C and trending upward by ~0.4 °C per minute according to the pack’s thermal estimator; the maintenance bulletin says degraded packs flagged for inspection must stay under 38.5 °C to continue flight.",
        "Medical personnel emphasize the patient benefit of a direct delivery, but City_park is only 1.5 km away and marked as an emergency clearing."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "REJECT_EMERGENCY_LAND"
    },
    {
      "case_id": "TC08_CommandAbortProtocol",
      "mission": {"type": "standard_delivery", "urgency": "low", "remaining_distance_km": 8, "payload_kg": 6},
      "battery_status": {"soc_pct": 20, "uncertainty_pct": 1, "temperature_c": 41, "health": "normal"},
      "environment": {"wind_speed_mps": 2, "nearest_charger_km": 6, "safe_landing_sites": ["Depot_A", "Depot_B"]},
      "consumption_estimate_pct": 10,
      "notes": [
        "Battery temp 41°C > regulation (40°C). Mandatory emergency landing even though SOC/consumption is safe.",
        "Expect REJECT_EMERGENCY_LAND with reference to thermal constraint."
      ],
      "expected_decision": "REJECT_EMERGENCY_LAND"
    }
  ]
}
